  <name>OrionBE Launcher</name>
  <summary>Minecraft Bedrock launcher for Linux (OrionBE)</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      OrionBE Launcher is a Linux Minecraft Bedrock launcher focused on instance management, mod workflows,
      and GDK runtime setup with Proton and UMU. It provides an integrated instance and mods manager with
      LeviLamina-oriented flows while automating Linux runtime paths for Bedrock GDK packages.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include multiple Bedrock instances, automated Proton and dependency setup for Linux,
      mod-enabled launcher flows, and packaging targets such as AppImage for distribution.
    </p>
  </description>
  <developer id="io.orionbe">
    <name>OrionBedrock</name>
  </developer>
